name: Webconsortium
overview:
We can support with new business opportunities

We are seeking for e-commerce businesses that are interested to develop new business opportunities or want to expand to or in Europe. We can assist you with new business opportunities, business models & strategies, finding the right location and employees, setting up the organization, local knowledge of sales and marketing and contacts in all the core success factors.

We are driven and entrepreneurial minded consultants that have the vision and skills to develop new business opportunities or can assist you with starting a business in a dissimilar market
